      <description>Leanita Shelby was a legislative assistant to Gillis Long between 1973
            and 1985. Gillis Long (1923-1985) was representative for the 8th U.S. Congressional
            District of Louisiana in 1963-1965 and 1973-1985. He ran unsuccessfully for governor of
            Louisiana in 1964 and 1971.</description>
